To compile and install Infernal Contractor II from this distribution:

Download and unpack the source and data files thus:

tar xvzf ic2-src-0_0_1.tar.gz
cd ic2-0.0.1
tar xvzf ic2-data-0_0_1.tar.gz

Run

./configure
(spend a few days getting the libraries which configure asks for)
make
make install

The application will be installed into to ic2data directory, not in the /usr tree.
It can then be run using

./ic2
